      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3588 - It is narrated from Al-Sakuni, from Abu Abdillah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that:\n\"He (as) used to forbid eating the walnuts that children bring from gambling, and He (as) said it is unlawful (suht).\""
